<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="79" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1436,613,676]" pageId="18" pageNumber="79">
Eight species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bischoff" authorityYear="1920" box="[339,472,613,639]" class="Insecta" family="Mutillidae" genus="Tropidotilla" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[339,472,613,639]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="79">Tropidotilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occur in the Palaearctic Region and six occur in the Afrotropical Region (
<bibRefCitation author="Pagliano, G. &amp; Brothers, D. J. &amp; Cambra, R. &amp; Lelej, A. S. &amp; Lo Cascio, P. &amp; Matteini Palmerini, M. &amp; Scaramozzino, P. L. &amp; Williams, K. A. &amp; Romano, M." pageId="18" pageNumber="79" pagination="5 - 425" refId="ref19407" refString="Pagliano, G., Brothers, D. J., Cambra, R., Lelej, A. S., Lo Cascio, P., Matteini Palmerini, M., Scaramozzino, P. L., Williams, K. A. &amp; Romano, M. (2020 [&quot; 2018 &quot;]) Checklist of names in Mutillidae (Hymenoptera), with illustrations of selected species. Bollettino del Museo Regionale di Scienze Naturali di Torino, 36 (1 - 2), 5 - 425." type="journal article" year="2020">
Pagliano 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="79">et al.</emphasis>
2020
</bibRefCitation>
). Three species of this genus are distributed in 
<collectingCountry box="[771,898,649,675]" name="Azerbaijan" pageId="18" pageNumber="79">Azerbaijan</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
